title: Video: Nautic – Fresh Eyes
body:
You like cats? I like cats.

**[Nautic](http://admin.crackintheroad.com/music/18297-new-nautic-fresh-eyes-ft-slime/ "New: Nautic – Fresh Eyes (ft. Slime)")** sure do like cats.

The video for **Nautic**’s debut track ‘_Fresh Eyes_’ dropped today. You should probably watch it.
